50|$|Ceiling tiles are {{lightweight}} tiles used inside buildings. They {{are placed}} in an aluminium grid; they provide little thermal insulation but are generally designed either to improve the <b>acoustics</b> <b>of</b> a <b>room</b> or to reduce the volume of air being heated or cooled.|$|R
