40|$|At the Department <b>of</b> <b>Acoustics</b> <b>of</b> the Fraunhofer IBP in Stuttgart, Germany the Research Group <b>of</b> Musical <b>Acoustics</b> deals {{mostly with}} pipe organ research. In {{the present paper}} some {{examples}} are shown on helping the voicing adjustments and sound design of labial organ pipes and {{on the work of}} matching the instrument to the <b>acoustics</b> <b>of</b> the <b>room...</b>|$|R
